data.description: Lovely townhome ready for immediate move in! This four year young townhome features wood floors, a kitchen with stainless steel appliances and upgraded counter tops, breakfast bar seating, overlooking the dining room that leads to the deck. A living room is just off the kitchen and a family room is located on the main level that could be a 4th bedroom also features a half bath. The 3rd floor includes the primary bedroom with one full bath and walk in closet, 2 more bedrooms and another full bathroom as well as the laundry. Fresh new carpet on main and 3rd floors. New paint throughout the entire home. The rear yard is fully fenced. The garage offers parking for 1 car and off street parking in the private driveway. Cedar Hill community includes a pool, gym (coming soon), tot lot, walking trails, dog park (coming soon), clubhouse/community center, sports courts and a pavilion area. LOTS of restaurants, shopping and grocery near by. Easy commute to 100, 97, 695, 295 and BWI.
